@Node DS911 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/DS9/The Nagus"

  @{b}The Nagus@{ub}

Quark receives a suprise - and something of a dubious honor - when
Grand Nagus Zek, a Ferengi business mogul, arrives at DS9. After
some customary patronizing at Quark's, Zek insists on holding a 
conference of Ferengi profiteers there, while Quark fears that Zek
plans on nuying out his bar on the station. To everyone's surprise,
especially Quark's, Zek announces his retirement and declares that
Quark will succeed him to the coveted position of Grand Nagus. Many
of the visiting Ferengi are jealous, as would be expected of them.
But Quark discovers - after a close call - that someone among the
Ferengi is jealous enough to try gaining the position of Nagus by
killing him.


