before the surviving Miradorn can exact vengeance, but Croden, the
visitor from the distant planet Rakhar troubles Odo even more, for
he may have a clue to the shapeshifter's origins in the Gamma
Quadrant. Odo must decide whether or not to trust the criminal
when Sisko orders him to transport Croden back through the wormhole
to Rakhar - and the surviving Miradorn brother leaves DS9 to follow
