imaginations, ranging from a favorite baseball player of Sisko's to
a pair of ravishing beauties (appearing, naturally, on Quark's arms)
to the girl of Bashir's dreams - Dax, but with a far different
personality. At first the apparitions seem harmless, but it then
seems that they are capable of posing danger to the crew.


