A Klingon ship makes an unexpected return from a scientific mission
in the Gamma Quadrant and self-destructs. A single member of the ship's
crew beams himself into Ops, dying shortly after cryptically announcing
"victory". As Dax and O'Brien start trying to piece together the 
mystery of the Klingon ship, divisions take place between members of
DS9'c crew. Kira, still unsatisfied after losing an argument with Sisko
about security arrangements for a shipload of possible allies of the
Cardassians, begins to plot against the commander, quietly gathering
loyal followers among the crew and threatening those who don't sympathize
with her cause. Sisko, in the meantime, goes into hiding supposedly for
security reasons, as he and Chief O'Brien prepare for Kira's imminent
mutiny. Odo remains the only officer who hasn't taken up arms with
either side yet, since he has his own motive.


