hazardous stellar ignition experiment under the auspices of Dr. Seyetik -
whose wife, as it so happens, turns out be Fenna... or a duplicate of
her. En route to the potentially deadly site of a dead star via the
Prometheus, Sisko struggles to decipher Fenna's secret.


