Kira sets off for Bajor when it is revealed that her memories of a
specific event in the Cardassian occupation differ with the official
records of the Bajoran central archives. She never makes it to the
archives, however, because she is captured and transported to Cardassia
Prime, where she wakes up with the features of a Cardassian. She is
