from Bajor to inform Sisko - still regarded as the Emissary in Bajoran culture -
that prophecy predicts the Cardassians' presence will result in calamity, not
the least of which will be the closure of the wormhole. As the mission progesses,
it all starts adding up as prophesied, including the appearance of a comet which
could damage or destroy the wormhole.


