usually elusive Cardassian tailor. One lead indicates it could be the work of a
Flaxian assassin, but the moment Odo tails the suspect's spacecraft. it is
destroyed by the Romulans who claim he was on their wanted list. Odo takes a
solo trip to a rendezvous with a Cardasian who gives him some information - that
