Garak's hunch that Tain may also be an assassin's target, but they are intercepted
en route by a Romulan ship carrying Tain as a passenger. Tain invites Garak to
rejoin him on a joint mission of the Obsidian Order and the Romulan Tal Shiar to
attack the Founder of the Dominion on their own turf - and Garak accepts.


