reveals he was shot by a TR-116 rifle, a weapon developed but never mass-produced
by Starfleet. Meanwhile, Ezri confronts one of Dax's previous incarnations in a
dream: Joran, a self-professed murderer, urges Ezri to channel his disturbing
memories and enable him to assist her in apprehending Ilario's killer. When
Ezri awakens, she learns that a second murder has occurred.


