  @{b}Chimera@{ub}

Odo returns from a conference with an unexpected guest: a Changeling who tracked
and boarded his Runabout. Odo recognizes him as one of "the hundred" shapeshifters
who were, like himself, sent out as infants into the galaxy to learn about other
species. Back at the station, Sisko warily releases the visitor to Odo's custody.
The Changeling, known as Laas, queries Odo about their unique species - with which
Laas has made no contact since his infancy - and "the Link", a Changeling ritual
that allows shapeshifters to meld with one another and thereby form a single,
sentient collective entity.


