@Node DS9165 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/DS9/Inter Arma Enim Silent Leges"

  @{b}Inter Arma Enim Silent Leges@{ub}

On the eve of Dr. Bashir's departure for a conference on the Romulan homeworld,
he's visited by Sloan, the director of Section 21, a secret and unsanctioned
extremist entity within Starfleet Intelligence. Sloan asks a reluctant Bashir
to gather information on the Romulan leadership. Bashir reports the request to
Sisko, who worries that although Starfleet Command has officially condemned
Section 31, someone in its membership may actually be protecting the group.
After consulting with Admiral Ross, Sisko advises Bashir to play along with
Sloan in order to determine Sloan's motivations.


