  @{b}The Dogs of War@{ub}

While Sisko takes command of a new ship named in honor of the Defiant,
Kira, Garak and Damar barely escape a Dominon ambush on Cardassia and are
forced into hiding. Quark receives a static-filled message from Grand Nagus
Zek, the Ferengi leader, that he's been named Zek's successor. Now cured of
the deadly Changeling virus, Odo is outraged to learn that he was infected
by Section 31 - an unsanctioned extremist organization within the Federation -
but promises Sisko he won't take matters into his own hands.


